<td><img class="tex" alt="\displaystyle \sqrt{2\pi}\cdot \delta(\omega)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/math/1/c/0/1c0f1933d86fa9d7fdf47036281b4866.png" /></td>
