<td><img class="tex" alt="\displaystyle \sqrt{\frac{\pi}{a}} \cos \left( \frac{\nu^2}{4 a} - \frac{\pi}{4} \right) " src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/math/a/0/f/a0f64d2b4973ef96fb7dfe6d10a0757d.png" /></td>
