</tr>
<tr>
<td>307</td>
<td><img class="tex" alt="\displaystyle \sin ( a x^2 ) \," src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/math/c/f/d/cfddc393642f859a31e239b40eced27a.png" /></td>
