<td><img class="tex" alt="\displaystyle \frac{-1}{\sqrt{2 a}} \sin \left( \frac{\omega^2}{4 a} - \frac{\pi}{4} \right) " src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/math/b/9/b/b9b64fc2435b0a93bad09ff12f6ae7b5.png" /></td>
