<li><span class="citation" id="CITEREFSteinShakarchi2003">Stein, Elias; Shakarchi, Rami (2003), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=FAOc24bTfGkC&amp;pg=PA158&amp;dq=%22The+mathematical+thrust+of+the+principle%22&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=Esa7T5PZIsqriQKluNjPDQ&amp;ved=0CDQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=%22The%20mathematical%20thrust%20of%20the%20principle%22&amp;f=false"><i>Fourier Analysis: An introduction</i></a>, Princeton University Press, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-691-11384-X" title="Special:BookSources/0-691-11384-X">0-691-11384-X</a><span class="printonly">, <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=FAOc24bTfGkC&amp;pg=PA158&amp;dq=%22The+mathematical+thrust+of+the+principle%22&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=Esa7T5PZIsqriQKluNjPDQ&amp;ved=0CDQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=%22The%20mathematical%20thrust%20of%20the%20principle%22&amp;f=false">https://books.google.com/books?id=FAOc24bTfGkC&amp;pg=PA158&amp;dq=%22The+mathematical+thrust+of+the+principle%22&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=Esa7T5PZIsqriQKluNjPDQ&amp;ved=0CDQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=%22The%20mathematical%20thrust%20of%20the%20principle%22&amp;f=false</a></span></span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Fourier+Analysis%3A+An+introduction&amp;rft.aulast=Stein&amp;rft.aufirst=Elias&amp;rft.au=Stein%2C%26%2332%3BElias&amp;rft.au=Shakarchi%2C%26%2332%3BRami&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pub=Princeton+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-691-11384-X&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DFAOc24bTfGkC%26pg%3DPA158%26dq%3D%2522The%2Bmathematical%2Bthrust%2Bof%2Bthe%2Bprinciple%2522%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ei%3DEsa7T5PZIsqriQKluNjPDQ%26ved%3D0CDQQ6AEwAA%23v%3Donepage%26q%3D%2522The%2520mathematical%2520thrust%2520of%2520the%2520princi